content.rendered:
Directed by Nila Madhab Panda.

Written by Protiqe Mojoomdar. Nila Madhab Panda. Rahul Ramchandani. Rahul Singh. Rahul Singh. Deepak Venkateshan. Deepak Venkateshan. Deepak Venkateshan.

Cast Kunal Kapoor(Raj). Radhika Apte(Paro). Saurabh Shukla(Braj Singh Deo). Gulshan Grover(Kharu Pahelwan – Co-lead) . Madhumita Barik(Bhulia’s wife). Harish Chhabra(Bhulia). Robin Das(Gopa). Vipin Katyal(Bachelor). Ekavali Khanna(Gulabo). Padam Mishra(Bachelor). Sahidur Rahaman(Dora). Anubha Sourya(Braj Singh Deo’s sister).Sushil Tyagi. Andy von Eich(Mr. Smith). Ram Naresh Diwakar(Biker 1 (uncredited))

Language Hindi.

Producers Bidhu Bhusan Panda. Bidhu Bhushan Panda. Nila Madhab Panda. Jacques Rajotte. Supratik Roy. Vasu Sharma.

Production Eleeanora Images.
